responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "37BC8AA5467CCD4341963FA344878C64", "Hail Citizen! It\'s far too dangerous out here for you commoners. Leave the protection of the roads to the Kaelar Army\'s Tower Guard. However, if you still wish to help, we need some water transported from the Crossroads Well to the posts. For Greater Glory!")
